portfolio_history

| id | timestamp | total_value |

news

| id | title | source | sentiment_score | related_symbol |

8️⃣ Architecture logique de l’IA

V1 = simple mais propre :

Score final = 
0.6 * score_technique
+ 0.4 * score_sentiment

Décision :

0.7 → BUY

< 0.3 → SELL

sinon HOLD

